Packages that use com.complexible.common.openrdf
com.complexible.common.openrdf This package defines classes for working with the Aduna OpenRdf framework 
 

Classes in com.complexible.common.openrdf used by com.complexible.common.openrdf
ConstrainedGraph
          A Graph which has a Constraint placed upon which statements can be added to the Graph.
DelegatingGraph
          Base class which implements the Graph interface, but delegates all operations to a sub-graph.
ExtGraph
          Extends the basic Sesame Graph interface to provide more concise access to various utility methods defined in Graphs or other interfaces as well as safer access to some methods that are functionally equivalent to what is defined in GraphUtil; nulls are not returned nor is GraphUtilException thrown for these methods.
ExtRepository
          Extends the normal Sesame Repository, via RepositoryWrapper, with some additional utility functions.
FunctionalGraph
          Convenience interface for a Sesame Graph for applying some of the Guava functional objects to a Graph.
ImmutableGraph
          An immutable version of an OpenRdf Graph
IOGraph
          Extends the standard Sesame Graph to provide some RDF IO methods for inserting data from input or writing the Graph out.
